{"tid":683141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[打J？]90後瞓身上車 自住舊樓帳面賺百萬！","createTime":"2018-05-29T12:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T07:11:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fe34a757f7976e5bc966d5b8ffca9723bdc11639","tid":683141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:35:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>90後講磚頭信念瞓身上車賺百萬</strong><br />\n九十後鄺加銘睇了過百個單位後，於一七年一月買入人生第一個物業，迄今帳面賺約百萬元，但當時他拿出戶口僅有的45萬元付首期和雜費，坦言「簽買賣合約時是不安多於興奮」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20180529/photo/0529-00269-001b1.jpg?t=1527597248182\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180529%2Fphoto%2F0529-00269-001b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1527597248182&h=acc7be1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他憶述，畢業後工作約兩年，就在25歲時首次置業：「這是位於<span style=\"color: red;\">佐敦的舊樓，當時樓齡39年</span>，實用面積約280方呎，成交價360萬元。我的買入呎價創了當時屋苑新高，所以決定後都有點擔心，但我相信磚頭可以保值，是相對穩定的投資工具。」結果，他買入後持有至今近一年半，<span style=\"color: red;\">自住單位已升值至約460萬元，升幅逾27%。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家也許羨慕加銘成功把握機會上車，但當時他以九成按揭買樓，計及經紀佣金、印花稅等後花了45萬元：「當時戶口冇晒錢，安全感少咗。過往食飯可以唔睇價錢，好食就得，飯後再同朋友飲酒花多幾百元都得。但買樓後一段短時間，食飯會揀平一點，可能30、40元就算。」<br />\n<br />\n然而，他指自己不會為上車而過分節衣縮食，因家人自小教他「錢不是儲回來，是搵回來的」，而他不算大使，不需要昂貴物質，亦不用很節儉地儲錢。<br />\n<br />\n不過，要搵到筍盤，還是要付出努力。加銘曾報讀物業投資課程，打好投資物業的基本功，然後再不斷睇樓。當時他睇了過百個單位，幾乎每日都睇，睇了3個月，終於被他找到這個佐敦單位，符合他的揀樓條件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20180529/00269_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180529%2F00269_001.html&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d2d3e1ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20180529/00269_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"88a2d5cd5dc0ad383f0e416fa5e5a84a99a924d5","tid":683141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">自住單位</span>已升值至約460萬元，升幅逾27%"},{"pid":"05c9308175b1636b5013a1d4c1d4941aad0f33a4","tid":683141,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"88a2d5cd5dc0ad383f0e416fa5e5a84a99a924d5","tid":683141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">自住單位</span>已升值至約460萬元，升幅逾27%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"自住黎講除咗差餉交多咗仲有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a4f59f26a1f609bb7318021b16d2a68dc3c463","tid":683141,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a2d5cd5dc0ad383f0e416fa5e5a84a99a924d5","tid":683141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">自住單位</span>已升值至約460萬元，升幅逾27%"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"公屋 better?"},{"pid":"bf02f2c4a472e9d7c0195f47985bbe11128f3397","tid":683141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45a4f59f26a1f609bb7318021b16d2a68dc3c463","tid":683141,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a2d5cd5dc0ad383f0e416fa5e5a84a99a924d5","tid":683141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">自住單位</span>已升值至約460萬元，升幅逾27%"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"公屋 better?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"yes<br />\n<br />\n全包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812d202ac666084849e5d583bbe5b0330cdeb79f","tid":683141,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"仲未駛俾錢維修咩？"},{"pid":"201543673d45280a9396ce6d8603e86245ae67a0","tid":683141,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93419580d06bf3690b24644704e6f99358999a5b","tid":683141,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":